            // Loop through each file to add it as required, needed for searching all directories in a tree structure   .     These are available by default at start of Java’s version and above versions (Java's Version Independence).  This loop iterates over the list ie array/set collecting files into our result set.
            // Loop through each file to add it as required, needed for maintaining all directories in a structure   .     These are available by default at start of Java’s version and above versions (Java's Version Independence).  It loops over the list ie array/set collecting files into our result set.
